title: (x) Almost Comic Sans - High Speed Braces - Comic Sans {self (Jenna A)}
content:
Hello I have been trying to figure out what this typeface is.  
It reminds me of Comic Sans but I don’t believe it is.  
If anyone could help that would be greatly appreciated.  
Thanks
